<member
><guiicon
><inlinemediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata fileref="list-add-22.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
></inlinemediaobject
></guiicon
> Добавить цель</member>
<member
><guiicon
><inlinemediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata fileref="document-new-22.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
></inlinemediaobject
></guiicon
> Создать набор целей</member>
<member
><guiicon
><inlinemediaobject
><imageobject
